{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["梦幻的交汇-日常篇\n\n<size=45>四　致姐姐大人…<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"初次见面，异世界的各位——我是本日前来助战的皇家荣耀，胡德。这位是我的随从…","dir":1,"bgm":"story-uta","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":204030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"那个…咱，咱是…小天鹅。那个，这个……请多指教…","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":201100},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"小天鹅，来站到这儿来。不可以一天到晚躲在我后面哦","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"诶诶诶…就算胡德姐姐你这么说……咱也不知道怎么…怎么和初次见面的人说话啊……","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"啊啦啊啦，又是一对感情深厚的姐妹登场了呢。真是倍感亲切","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300060},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"是……吗","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300010},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"但是这两位的话……不是更像久远大人和猫音大人吗？","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"诶？我和姐姐大人的关系，在你们眼里是这样的吗？","actor":10300020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"我觉得我们的关系更自然一些啊…对吧猫音","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"正是如此，姐姐大人","actor":10300020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"我已经听说各位的情况了。原来的世界里有很重要的伙伴在等着你们…所以各位才会如此归心似箭，情有可原。","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"换作是我，如果小天鹅出了什么事的话，我也会不顾三七二十一立刻赶去帮她吧","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"胡，胡德姐姐，居然这么关心咱…啊，诶？怎么突然凑过来…","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":201100},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"当然，不仅是小天鹅，不管是学院里的谁遇上了难事，我也发誓我会立刻前去帮忙的","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"唔诶诶诶…胡德姐姐，凑太近啦！这么贴着咱的话，咱会害羞的……","dir":1,"side":1,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.4,"number":2,"x":22.5}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":201100},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"那，那个！就算都是女孩子，也不好在别人面前贴这么紧吧……！","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"该说是女孩子…还是大姐姐呢……","actor":101170,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"拉菲，这个话题不要说下去了","actor":401230,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"年龄微妙呢","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300040},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"女孩子不管几岁都不能忘记作为少女的内心，母亲大人一直这么教导我们","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300050},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"那不是……女性不管几岁都喜欢可爱的东西的意思吗，对吧？","actor":10300020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"就算你问我我也……不知道该说什么","actor":301050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"啊，呃……对，对了！为了和各位好好聊一聊，我带了这个……（摸索摸索","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"请！请大家尝尝看这个……咱老家送来的……红薯！","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"红薯……吗？诶，这不是……","actor":10300010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"哎呀，这不是莫洛洛吗。虽然颜色不一样","actor":10300060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"呃，诶……莫洛洛？","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"恩，和我们祖国常见的农作物十分相似呢。虽然形状稍有不同颜色也比较深……不过果然是莫洛洛吧","actor":10300010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"所以这应该是——红莫洛洛吧","actor":10300060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"小天鹅，谢谢你给我们带粮食来。那就让我们好好尝尝吧。","actor":10300010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"啊，嗯……你们高兴的话，咱也很高兴……诶嘿嘿","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"军粮乃战场不可或缺之物……小天鹅，这次你干的不错哦","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":204030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"被胡德姐姐夸奖了……诶嘿嘿。回去以后可得打个电话给老家说声谢谢呢……","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"那这样吧。作为奖励，就送小天鹅一套全新的圣诞衣装吧","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"——唔诶诶？！","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"绝对不输去年的那套哦……呵呵，你可得好好期待着哦，小天鹅？","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"诶诶诶诶？！又要穿那种丢人现眼的衣服吗……求求你饶了咱吧","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"……怎么说呢，看着小天鹅这样我怎么觉得一点也不陌生","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"是啊……胡德大人也和卡露拉妈…姐姐大人似的呢","actor":10300060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"就是久远大人的数位母亲之一的那位卡露拉大人吗？……原来是那种感觉的人啊","actor":10300030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"胡德姐姐看上去也是那种好事坏事都要去管一下的感觉呢","actor":10300020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"你这么一说……胡德小姐的确常常照顾我们呢","actor":201210,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"恩，喜欢照顾人……而且尤其喜欢照顾小天鹅……","actor":101170,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"但是前段时间……阿贝克隆比把胡德小姐叫做胡德阿yi…","actor":301050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"——眼神一闪！","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":204030,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"{namecode:6}酱，你说什么了吗？","actor":204030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"没，我什么都……没说","actor":301050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"禁语","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300040},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"说出那个词的瞬间便感知到了与解放者之怒相匹敌的怒火。还请慎言。","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","actor":10300050},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"居然能和那种吓人的神明的怒火相匹敌吗？！","actor":201210,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"少女心受伤带来的怒火，就是这种等级的东西呢","actor":10300060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"……真是让人想起卡露拉妈……姐姐大人呢……","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":10300010,"bgName":"bg_story_chuansong","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"LINKPREHEAT21","fadeOut":1.5}